^#99BBFF;The Spirit Guardian^reset; is a lifeform that exists within plants and animals. They are active, kind, and helpful creatures. Once their homeland has enough Spirit Trees to maintain the balance of the ecosystem, they will turn their attention to further worlds, in hopes of finding lands that require their power.

  ^orange;Diet:^reset; Herbivorous

